um" alt="" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Bs-1-290x192.jpg 290w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Bs-1-1024x678.jpg 1024w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Bs-1-270x178.jpg 270w" sizes="(max-width: 290px) 100vw, 290px" /></li><li class="gallery-item"><img width="290" height="192" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Bs-2-290x192.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium" alt="" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Bs-2-290x192.jpg 290w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Bs-2-1024x678.jpg 1024w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Bs-2-270x178.jpg 270w" sizes="(max-width: 290px) 100vw, 290px" /></li><li class="gallery-item"><img width="132" height="200" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Bs-3-132x200.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium" alt="" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Bs-3-132x200.jpg 132w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Bs-3-508x768.jpg 508w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Bs-3-270x407.jpg 270w" sizes="(max-width: 132px) 100vw, 132px" /></li></ul></div></div></p> <a class="wpptopdf" target="_blank" rel="noindex,nofollow" href="http://www.gbopera.it/2011/12/brescia-teatro-grande-il-barbiere-di-siviglia/?format=pdf" title="Download PDF"><img alt="Download PDF" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/plugins/wp-post-to-pdf/asset/images/pdf.png"></a></div><div class="clear"></div><div class="entry-extra clearfix"><div class="comments-link " style="color: #363636"> <i class="icon-comment"></i> <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2011/12/brescia-teatro-grande-il-barbiere-di-siviglia/#comments">1 Reply</a></div><div class="entry-share"> <span style="color: #363636">Share This<i class="icon-plus"></i></span><div class="entry-share-icons"> <span class="ct-pinterest" title="Share on Pinterest"><a href="http://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=http://www.gbopera.it/201